			icons: icons.map(val => ({data:val})),
			search: '',
			//items: new Array(1000).fill(0).map((_, index) => ({ data: '#' + index }))
		}
	},
	computed: {
		iconsFiltered() {
			return this.icons.filter(({data}) => data.toString().toLowerCase().indexOf(this.search.toString().toLowerCase()) !== -1)
		}	
	},
	methods: {
		cellSizeAndPositionGetter(item, index) {
			// compute size and position
			return {
				width: this.iconSize,
				height: this.iconSize,
				x: (index % this.itemsInRow) * this.iconSize,
				y: parseInt(index / this.itemsInRow) * this.iconSize
			}
		},
		calcDims() {
			if(window.innerWidth <= 768) {
				this.iconSize = 131
			} else {
				this.iconSize = 164
			}

			this.width  = document.getElementById('icons-wrapper').clientWidth
			this.height = document.getElementById('icons-wrapper').clientHeight
			if(window.innerWidth <= 768) {
				this.height = document.getElementById('page-icons').clientHeight - 30
			}

			this.itemsInRow = Math.floor((this.width - 16) / this.iconSize)

			this.asyncComponent = 'VirtualCollection'
		},
		handleResize: _.throttle(function (e) {
			this.asyncComponent = null
			setTimeout(this.calcDims,1000)
		}, 500)
	},
	mounted() {
		this.calcDims()		
	}
